make
make run 
OR
./main <num_imipressions> <path_to_input_files>
e.g. ./main 4096 ../inputs/adpredictor

Note that input files need to be larger (or the same size) as the problem size called. It is easiest to generate very large inputs once (~10,000,000) and use this for all execution.

________________________________________________________________________________
To generate input impressions (from old adp project):

% mkdir inputs
% make gen_inputs
% ./gen_inputs <num_impressions>
